Packages 
Package Description
aquarium
Contains the Aquarium manager class and subpackages for Aquarium resources, such as UI and the creatures that go in the Aquarium.
aquarium.creatures
Contains the collection of classes implementing Creature which are then added to the Aquarium.
aquarium.ui
UI classes used by AquariumMain and the Aquarium class.
